    small = min(a, b)
    while not big % small == 0:
        big, small = small, big%small
    return small

#include <iostream>                                             
using namespace std;                                            
                                                                
int GCD(int a,int b) {                                          
  if (a<=b) {                                                   
    swap(a,b);                                                  
  }                                                             
  if (b==0) {                                                   
    return a;                                                   
  }                                                             
  return GCD(b,a%b);                                            
}                                                               
                                                                
int main() {                                                    
  int x, y;                                                     
  cin >> x >> y;                                                
  cout << GCD(x,y) << endl;                                     
  return 0;                                                     
}

#include <iostream>                                             
using namespace std;                                            
                                                                
int gcd(int a,int b) {                                          
  if (a<b) {                                                    
    swap(a,b);                                                  
  }                                                             
  if (b==0) {                                                   
    return a;                                                   
  }                                                             
  return gcd(b,a%b);                                            
}                                                               
                                                                
int main(void) {                                                
  int x, y;                                                     
  cin >> x >> y;                                                
  cout << gcd(x,y) << endl;                                     
  return 0;                                                     
}
